Transcript: Good evening. You, as a member of the Etobicoke Lakeshore Liberal Association are requested to attend a nomination meeting tomorrow, Wednesday, November 30th at 5:30 p.m. at the Valhalla Inn in Etobicoke at number 1 Valhalla Inn Road, one block south of Brunethorpe. turn west off the East Mall.
